title: JRE REVIEW of 1303 with Tommy Chong
description:
Tommy Chong is a legend of the marijuana community. Star of the Cheech and Chong movies. He's now 81 years old and still trucking on. He has a really chilled conversation with Joe and shares a lot of stories from his life. This was a pleasure to review.
